    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## How to use（In this section, show an example to submit a long video (at least 1 minute) for getting AI clips via API）\n1.  Obtain Your API Key, and repalce VIZARDAI_API_KEY of headers of node 'video clip create workflow' and ' vizard video clip query workflow'.\n2. Submit a Video for Clipping ( https://docs.vizard.ai/docs/basic ).\n3. Retrieve Your Clips（ https://docs.vizard.ai/docs/retrieve-video-clips ）.\n4. Check clip status by polling, or configure a webhook URL in workspace before submitting a video.\n##\n\nQuick start：https://docs.vizard.ai/docs/quickstart\nThe maximum video length is 600 minutes, with a file size limit of 10GB. The highest supported upload resolution is 4K, and exported clips will maintain the same resolution as the original long video.",
